cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE, cs.DC 

This paper is about graph convolutional neural networks (GCNs) and their execution on GPUs. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since GCNs are commonly used in these fields. Additionally, since the paper explores hardware optimization, cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) is also a likely category. Finally, since the paper discusses software optimization, cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is a possible category as well.
